title: Transformer Fitzroy
typeOfFood: Lacto, Organic, Western, Mediterranean, Beer/Wine, Australian
description: Vegetarian restaurant and bar opened Mar 2015 by the owners of Vegie Bar and Rice Queen. Has courtyard and dining for up to 100. On the menu are experimental dishes like king oyster mushroom with confit garlic pine-nut puree and smoked shallot, plus cocktails and pressed juices. Many dishes are vegan or have vegan option including almond feta and vegan mayo.
